summary: This module offers an annotation based Kubernetes extension implementation for Ballerina.
description:
Module Overview

This module offers an annotation based Kubernetes extension implementation for Ballerina.

  • For more information on the deployment, see the Kubernetes Deployment Guide.
  • For examples on the usage of the operations, see the AWS Lambda Deployment Example.

Annotation Usage Sample:

import ballerina/http;
import ballerina/log;
import ballerinax/kubernetes;

@kubernetes:Ingress{
    hostname: "abc.com"
}
@kubernetes:Service {
    name:"hello"
}
listener http:Listener helloEP = new(9090);

@kubernetes:Deployment {
    livenessProbe: true
}
@http:ServiceConfig {
    basePath: "/helloWorld"
}
service helloWorld on helloEP {
    resource function sayHello(http:Caller caller, http:Request request) {
        http:Response response = new;
        response.setTextPayload("Hello, World from service helloWorld ! ");
        var responseResult = caller->respond(response);
        if (responseResult is error) {
            log:printError("error responding back to client.", err = responseResult);
        }
    }
}

fields.name: dockerHost
fields.description: Docker host IP and docker PORT. (e.g minikube IP and docker PORT). Default is to use DOCKER_HOST environment variable. If DOCKER_HOST is unavailable, use "unix:///var/run/docker.sock" for Unix or use "npipe:////./pipe/docker_engine" for Windows 10 or use "localhost:2375".

fields.name: dockerCertPath
fields.description: Docker certificate path. Default is "DOCKER_CERT_PATH" environment variable.

fields.name: baseImage
fields.description: Base image to create the docker image. Default value is "openjdk:8-jre-alpine".

fields.name: image
fields.description: Docker image name with tag. Default is "<OUTPUT_FILE_NAME>:latest". If field registry is set then it will be prepended to the docker image name as <registry>/<OUTPUT_FILE_NAME>:latest.

fields.name: buildImage
fields.description: Docker image to be build or not. Default is true.

fields.name: push
fields.description: Enable pushing docker image to registry. Field buildImage must be set to true to be effective. Default value is false.

fields.name: cmd
fields.description: Value for CMD for the generated Dockerfile. Default is CMD java -jar ${APP} [--b7a.config.file=${CONFIG_FILE}] [--debug].

fields.name: copyFiles
fields.description: Array of file configurations for the Docker image.

fields.name: singleYAML
fields.description: Generate a single yaml file with all kubernetes artifacts (services, deployment, ingress and etc). Default is true.

fields.name: namespace
fields.description: Kubernetes namespace to be used on all artifacts.

fields.name: livenessProbe
fields.description: Enable/Disable liveness probe and configure it. Default is false.

fields.name: readinessProbe
fields.description: Enable/Disable readiness probe and configure it. Default is false.

fields.name: sourceFile
fields.description: source path of the file (in your machine)

fields.name: hostname
fields.description: Host name of the ingress. Default is "<BALLERINA_SERVICE_NAME>.com" or "<BALLERINA_SERVICE_LISTENER_NAME>.com".

fields.name: singleYAML

fields.name: forcePullDockerImage
fields.description: Set force pull images when building docker image.

fields.name: buildDockerWithNoCache
fields.description: Build docker image with no cache enabled.

fields.name: cpuPercentage
fields.description: CPU percentage to start scaling. Default is 50.

fields.name: operator
fields.description: Operator between the key and value. Default is "Equal".

fields.name: tolerationSeconds
fields.description: Time period of toleration in seconds. Default is 0.

fields.name: serviceType
fields.description: Service type of the service. Default is "ClusterIP".

fields.name: nodePort
fields.description: NodePort for the pods. Default is not set.

records.name: RollingUpdateConfig
records.description: Rolling Update config type field for deployment.

fields.name: data
fields.description: Paths to data files as an array.

fields.name: portName
fields.description: Name for the port. Default value is the protocol of the listener.

fields.name: port
fields.description: Service port. Default is the Ballerina service port.

constants.name: IMAGE_PULL_POLICY_IF_NOT_PRESENT
constants.description: Pull image if it is not present for deployment or job.

constants.name: IMAGE_PULL_POLICY_ALWAYS
constants.description: Always pull the image for knative service for deployment or job.

constants.name: IMAGE_PULL_POLICY_NEVER
constants.description: Never pull the image for deployment or job.

constants.name: RESTART_POLICY_ALWAYS
constants.description: Always restart policy when job is finished.
